1. *Ostali* su odlučili da se presele u drugu zemlju. (The rest decided to move to another country.)

2. Svi su otišli, a *ostali* su samo oni. (Everyone left, but only they remained.)

3. *Ostale* su im stvari u kući. (Their things remained in the house.)

4. *Ostalom* delu sveta se ne pridaje dovoljna pažnja. (The rest of the world is not given enough attention.)

5. *Ostali* su se udaljili od centra grada. (They moved away from the city centre.)